===Proper noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''[[Triangulum]] [[galaxy|Galaxy]]'''

#{{astronomy}}: A relatively nearby [[spiral]] [[galaxy]] in the [[Local Group]], together with the [[Milky Way]] galaxy. It is at a distance of approximately 2.6 million [[light year]]s from Earth, in the direction of the [[constellation]] [[Triangulum]].

